    <div class="home-page-description">
        <h1>Welcome to Your To-Do List!</h1>
        <p class="intro-text">
            Organize your tasks, set priorities, and manage your time effortlessly.
        </p>
    
        <h2>Features at a Glance:</h2>
        <ul class="features-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i> <span class="feature-title">Dashboard Overview:</span> Get a quick snapshot of all your tasks, including the most important and urgent ones.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> <span class="feature-title">Upcoming Tasks:</span> Keep track of what's coming up next with tasks that are just around the corner.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i> <span class="feature-title">Overdue Tasks:</span> Easily spot and handle tasks that are past their due dates.</li>
