            <li><i class="fas fa-list-alt"></i> <span class="feature-title">Custom Lists:</span> Organize your tasks into custom categories like Work, Personal, or any other list you create.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-star"></i> <span class="feature-title">Priority Levels:</span> Assign priorities to your tasks: Low, Mid, and High.</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i> <span class="feature-title">Add New Tasks and Lists:</span> Easily add tasks and create new lists to stay organized.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
